17
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:30,599
Looks like...

18
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,520
his mind's been replaced with

19
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,439
my original memories.

20
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,840
Just now was probably

21
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,599
an unconscious reaction to the recent switch.

22
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:41,479
I'm here to

23
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,159
