24
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:45,840
Tell me.

25
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:48,599
How much do you need?

26
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,759
Sheng Yuanzhou, what are you doing here?

27
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:53,439
Bullying our Xiaobei...

28
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,199
