30
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:01,319
Now you won't even spare my only son?

31
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,759
Ma'am, I... I'm here to...

32
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,280
I'm here to pay your medical bills.

33
