45
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,520
He looked so pitiful.

46
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:30,759
Mom!

47
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:33,000
If anything happens to him,

48
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:37,039
