49
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:38,439
Mom!

50
00:03:46,039 --> 00:03:46,400
Mom!

51
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:47,400
Doctor!

52
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:48,560
Doctor, hurry! Doctor!

53
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,120
Mom!

54
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,280
Doctor, hurry, hurry!

55
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:50,879
Hurry!

56
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:52,719
Mom, hang in there! Mom!

57
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:55,560
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

58
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,319
Here!

59
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:15,639
That 100,000 is my mom's life-saving money!

60
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:18,160
Please give it back to me, okay?

61
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,360
I'm begging you!

62
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,399
Please give it back!

63
00:04:37,639 --> 00:04:39,839
So this is the power of money.

64
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:42,439
It can save lives... and change fate.

65
00:04:50,639 --> 00:04:51,120
Mr. Sheng.

66
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,959
I've paid the surgery and hospital fees in full.

67
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,199
I also left your card number on file.

68
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,000
Any further expenses will be deducted directly.

69
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:58,439
Thank you.

70
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,680
The Chairman is still waiting for you to return.

71
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:12,160
You even paid their medical bills?

72
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,720
Call it hush money.

73
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,879
After all, they got a video of me injuring someone.

74
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:20,160
Give them some money,

75
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,879
so they won't run their mouths.

76
00:05:24,519 --> 00:05:25,199
It's late.

77
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,639
Go get some sleep.

78
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,319
Okay, Dad.

79
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,360
You should get some rest too.

80
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,319
Wait.

81
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,199
Since when did you start

82
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:34,560
