83
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:57,079
Remember.

84
00:05:58,439 --> 00:05:59,959
From now on, call me Father.

85
00:06:05,519 --> 00:06:07,160
She should get better soon.

86
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:08,920
Yes, Father.

87
00:06:55,079 --> 00:06:56,600
So there really is

88
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,759
