97
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,560
Thirty days.

98
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:41,319
I've got to make the most of these 30 days

99
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,800
to change my family's fate.

100
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,279
Good morning, Young Master.

101
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,199
Morning, morning, morning.

102
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:03,040
Young Master, today's flowers were airlifted from the UK.

103
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,800
They were delivered directly to our central garden.

104
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:06,120
If you don't like them,

105
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,160
