109
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,679
No, it hasn't.

110
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:22,879
It's delicious.

111
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:27,200
Have some water.

112
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:48,960
Father, you wanted to see me?

113
00:09:50,519 --> 00:09:52,559
Your performance lately is still just average.

114
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,879
