116
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:02,320
Zhu Zipeng.

117
00:10:06,799 --> 00:10:07,919
Zhu Zipeng.

118
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:09,600
A young entrepreneur.

119
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,360
Returned from studying abroad.

120
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,639
With his parents' resources behind him,

121
00:10:13,639 --> 00:10:15,440
