163
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,320
I was wrong.

164
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,159
I heard you.

165
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:57,919
I was wrong.

166
00:11:58,639 --> 00:11:59,159
I was wrong!

167
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:09,519
